_sText:
I made this in about 4 hours, before you ask, yes there are no triggers apart from teleports, why?
because even on legit, you're going to get a terrible time when you don't bhop and that is what this is about.

The seamless teleport thing with levels connected like that was inspired by bhop_fresh (which is why I started making this).

There is a bonus if you noclip up from the last level you will find it in the sky.
